import React from 'react'
import './Hindi.css'
import Navbar from '../../Components/Navbar/Navbar'
import Footer from '../../Components/Footer/Footer'
import Units from '../../Components/Units/Units'

const Hindi = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <Navbar/>

        <Units language/>

        <Footer/>
    </>
  )
}

export default Hindi
